I KNOW WHAT IT WAS.

49:14.785 --> 49:17.026
I REMEMBER IT NOW.

49:17.872 --> 49:20.364
I DON'T KNOW WHAT HAPPENED
TO YOU, EITHER, HORACE,

49:20.458 --> 49:23.450
BUT I THINK WE'RE
ALL LIKE THAT.

49:23.502 --> 49:28.793
<i>WE REMEMBER WHAT WAS GOOD, AND
WE BLACK OUT WHAT WAS BAD,</i>

49:28.841 --> 49:31.629
MAYBE BECAUSE WE
COULDN'T LIVE IF WE DIDN'T.

49:34.221 --> 49:36.303
LET'S GO HOME. THERE'S
A PARTY WAITING.

49:59.371 --> 50:01.863
<i>(narrator) EXIT MR. AND MRS.
HORACE FORD,</i>

50:01.957 --> 50:03.914
<i>WHO HAVE LIVED
THROUGH A BIZARRE MOMENT</i>

50:04.001 --> 50:07.335
<i>NOT TO BE CALIBRATED ON
NORMAL CLOCKS OR WATCHES.</i>

50:07.421 --> 50:09.537
<i>TIME HAS PASSED,
TO BE SURE,</i>

50:09.632 --> 50:12.374
<i>BUT IT'S THE SPECIAL TIME
IN THE SPECIAL PLACE</i>

50:12.468 --> 50:14.675
<i>KNOWN AS
THE TWILIGHT ZONE.</i>

50:20.893 --> 50:23.510
<i>[eerie music]</i>
